{"tid":1250020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩你地班無係現場既人唔好開post落order叫現場既人點點點","createTime":"2019-06-22T02:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T05:16:02.000Z","uid":84267,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8c25c60f0dfff4c1d01169681b8fd5b03b93d7","tid":1250020,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:12:57.000Z","msg":"已經見得太多<br />\n唔喺現場既巴絲, 唔知乜野情況既就咪做鍵盤指揮啦. 要去邊, 幾時走, 現場既人會自己討論搞掂啦. <br />\n發出提議討論係好, 但如果你個post係有幫人做決定既感覺, 只會令在場既人反感<br />\n<br />\n連登已經夠多五毛分化post, 散播假消息同失敗言論. 所以嗰D態度同意見好強硬既post根本就好類似. <br />\n<br />\n我地可以做既, 就係負評同屌鳩五毛post, 同推正路post. <br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位, 我唔想話咩人係五毛, 但唔理你有心定無心都好, 唔在場既人唔該唔好諗住幫人做決定."},{"pid":"2dc48268cc92af4b5ebfc7343643ed2e9aea6233","tid":1250020,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:44:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3665203f9f18d6e4403bb6d85bced344c520f61d","tid":1250020,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:57:53.000Z","msg":"冇錯 我都係咁講<br />\n點做都支持佢地"},{"pid":"ca4d065cd2535757fe4442b052edd29054ed455b","tid":1250020,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:27:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6068b43a2da6d1949530ad5cb567a627e80396cb","tid":1250020,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:03:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be838ecdf3124ff26bbd3dae073c7fb81e008a31","tid":1250020,"uid":58669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:04:40.000Z","msg":"TG 呢"},{"pid":"71d6a1e67d3077d03f445244c614246ca9f692d8","tid":1250020,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:05:53.000Z","msg":"係現場根本無機會睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以一野就照到<br />\n各自爬山"},{"pid":"b2f111b35f25a2ca9851c55fe4cbdd86051c8cac","tid":1250020,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:09:37.000Z","msg":"係，提議就好"},{"pid":